        <mxCell id="wLMJtahLav3UEi4vTlQo-10" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" value="&lt;b&gt;Lite Performance&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;u&gt;CPU MidFreq as minfreq&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;cpu mid freq &amp;gt; scaling_min_freq&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;cpuinfo_max_freq &amp;gt; scaling_max_freq&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;GPU Midfreq as GPU minfreq&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;balanced misc tweaks&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;GOV is schedutil / Custom&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Note: This one is actually rebranding for Balanced in Game Assistant but yea, in game you know it&#39;s fcked up if I set it to normal (So set this as 4)&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
