        <mxCell id="wLMJtahLav3UEi4vTlQo-16" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" value="&lt;b&gt;Rules of Project Raco&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Assembly (only arm64) + C Scripts&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Do take a note that using shell is &lt;b&gt;PROHIBITED&lt;/b&gt; by any means&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Unless, it only can be done via shell, it is &lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;forgiveable&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;. But use it &lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;as minimal as it can&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- &lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Minimize the usage of dumpsys, cmd, etc&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;- Using UNIX socket is prohibited, please use POSIX (Direct execution)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;- Calling binary uses linker64&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;- It is adviseable for using su -c for once only task, if loop task please warp su -c for once execution so that will not call su -c on repeat&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="190" width="430" x="-670" y="20" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="wLMJtahLav3UEi4vTlQo-17" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontStyle=1" value="Game Assistant Features" vertex="1">
